metadata.title: ECS-SH-50-SAET 3.5 mm Stetho Style Transcription Headset with Soft Eartips
features: ECS SH-50 SAET Stetho Style Headset With Soft Eartips.
Compatible with transcribers requiring a single 3.5 mm mono plug such as SONY, Lanier, DVI, RTAS, Olympus, Panasonic and Sanyo.
Clear Plastic-Hinged stethoscope, tubular style with white ear tips using a single 3.5 mm right angle mono plug with 5 foot cord.
description: Compatible with transcribers requiring a single 3.5 mm mono jack such as SONY, Lanier, DVI, RTAS, Olympus, Panasonic, and Sanyo. Hinged stethoscope, tubular style with black soft ear tips using a single 3.5 mm right angle mono jack.
